        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Dear {!$Record.BLN_NominatedPerson__r.BLN_AccountName__c},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As you know, we wanted to be able to give you a full response to your complaint by now.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately, this is taking longer than we had hoped, but we plan to come back to you with a full response as soon as possible. We will continue to keep you updated, but if there’s anything you’d like to speak to us about please call me on 0344 826 8377.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I hope you’ll give us the time we need to complete our investigation, however I do need to let you know you now have the right to refer your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service, free of charge – but you must do so within six months of the date of this e-mail. Please note, there may be parts of your complaint which fall outside their remit.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you do not refer your complaint in time, the Financial Ombudsman Service will only have our permission to consider your complaint in very limited circumstances. For example, if the Financial Ombudsman Service believes the delay was as a result of exceptional circumstances.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Financial Ombudsman Service has a leaflet outlining how they may help you. This is available on their website at:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.financial-ombudsman.org.uk/publications/consumer-leaflet.htm&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: blue; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;http://www.financial-ombudsman.org.uk/publications/consumer-leaflet.htm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;. If you require a copy of this by post, please let us know by replying to this email.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Financial Ombudsman Service may be contacted via the following channels:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Post&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;: Financial Ombudsman Service, Exchange Tower, London, E14 9SR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Telephone:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;0800 023 4567&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Email&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:complaint.info@financial-ombudsman.org.uk&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: blue; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;complaint.info@financial-ombudsman.org.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Website:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.financial-ombudsman.org.uk/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: blue; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;www.financial-ombudsman.org.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yours sincerely&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!$Record.Owner:User.FirstName} {!$Record.Owner:User.LastName}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tel: 0344 826 8377&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Email: {!$Record.Owner:User.Email}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: medium; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;You can contact us between 8.30am and 5.30pm Monday to Friday. Calls may be recorded for training and monitoring purposes.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://belronint--ukdev2.sandbox.file.force.com/file-asset-public/Autoglass_logo?oid=00D7Z000000543T&quot; alt=&quot;Autoglass logo&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
